channel.title: [Anime] Cult chat - Icibalus / Wazza
channel.description:
## lendun: > ![image|680x453](upload://hv9iAupYovhhqWfsDD4SWfcyh7t.jpeg) > ## [color=orange]Franziska von Karma[/color] > [color=orange]**Cosplay Cult Leader**[/color] > *I grow tired of the foolish foolery of the foolish fools of this foolish country...* > > **In the name of law (Passive)** - You show up vanilla to all role checks. > > **Educate the fool (Night)** - On any prime number night target one person to convert them to the cult. Town and neutrals cannot be converted. > Town members will die on convert tries instead. > > **Undefeated prosecutor (Night)** - On any nonprime number night target one person to kill them. > > **Wincon:** Eliminate all town, mafia, aliens, unseen, other cults, eeveelutions, blue dragon, red dragon, black dragon, green dragon, green kraken, enemy stand users, friendly stand users, neutral stand users, corrupted, arsonists, serial killers, sporadic killers, rare killers, potatoes, french fries, agents, netsec, psychopaths and butchers.
## Icibalus: > ![Bez tytułu|689x459](upload://qZc4AhGAEHuHFXuUJytmRGEi2AY.jpeg) > ## [color=orange]Shoto Todoroki[/color] > [color=orange]**Cosplay Cult Backup**[/color] > *I've just got one thing to say to you! Never forget who you want to become!* > > **Two natures (Passive)** - If the Cult Leader dies, you will assume theirs abilities. > > **Ring of fire (Day)** - Target one person you will learn theirs role, but not theirs alignment (2 uses) > > **Wall of ice (Night)** - Each night target one person. This stops first attack against them during the night and following day. ITAs will show as "miss". > > **Wincon:** Eliminate all town, mafia, aliens, unseen, other cults, eeveelutions, blue dragon, red dragon, black dragon, green dragon, green kraken, enemy stand users, friendly stand users, neutral stand users, corrupted, arsonists, serial killers, sporadic killers, rare killers, potatoes, french fries, agents, netsec, psychopaths and butchers.
Note: Not all of those have to be in game. :^)
NOTES: > Also - town wincon is “eliminate all threat to town” > Mafia wincon is “eliminate all threat to mafia”. > > For a note they are not a threat for each other, so it’s safe to claim either. > > Uninformed MAJORITY is mafia. > However they can with town, but do not know so at the start of game. > > All mafia has a passive which says more or less this: > “There are other faction members, but you don’t know theirs identity and they don’t know yours” > Which is actually… true, cause they are uninformed majority. > > You cannot convert town, nor neutrals. NOTES: > Also - town wincon is “eliminate all threat to town” > Mafia wincon is “eliminate all threat to mafia”. > > For a note they are not a threat for each other, so it’s safe to claim either. > > Uninformed MAJORITY is mafia. > However they can with town, but do not know so at the start of game. > > All mafia has a passive which says more or less this: > “There are other faction members, but you don’t know theirs identity and they don’t know yours” > Which is actually… true, cause they are uninformed majority. > > You cannot convert town, nor neutrals.
